### **4. 2_StreamLinePlotter**  
**Description:**  
A real-time chart viewer that plots data as it streams into the terminal.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamLinePlotter - Real-Time Line Chart Viewer

StreamLinePlotter visualizes numeric data streams with live updates to a graph.

## Features
- Real-time graphing  
- Adjustable speed and range  
- Easy to integrate  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/2_StreamLinePlotter.git
cd 2_StreamLinePlotter
python visualize.py
